title: DAZ3D - Poser - LY Evie (DAZ 20036) DIM G2F
description:
Evie is an alluring, graceful stunner. With classic good looks and an athletic body, she is sure to bring a touch of elegance to your renders. This classy girl was specifically designed for Genesis 2 Female.

Evie comes with DAZ Studio Sub-Surface Scatter Materials, nine natural eye colors. She also comes with 10 makeups (plus a nude option), 10 lipsticks (plus a nude option),and 10 nail fashionable colors and designs.

Included are Quick Start areas to get you going fast... full body morphs together with texture, 11 preset makeup combos which include matching makeup, lips and nails.... you can change around them however you want... no hard and fast sets. Just a suggestion of where to start. All of this to make getting started faster, so you can focus on making art.

Evie measurements courtesy of Measure Metrics for DAZ Studio:

Height: 5' 7.5" (1.71 m)
Bust Circumference: 35.0" - 32C (88.9 cm - 70D)
Waist Circumference: 24.0" (60.9 cm)
Low Hip Circumference: 35.1" (89.1 cm)
